results.name: Triangle read by rows, the coefficients of the inverse partial P-polynomials.
comment: The triangle of coefficients of the partial P-polynomials is A269941. For the definition of the inverse partial P-polynomials see the link 'P-transform'.
example: Replacing the sublists by their sums reduces the triangle to a signed version of the triangle A097805. The column 1 of sublists is A111785 in a different order.
results.author: _Peter Luschny_, Mar 08 2016
